claim: Adele sings all the songs from the album 25.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The programme featured Adele and her live band performing songs from her repertoire and third studio album 25  (  2015  )  , as well as other songs from her other two albums , 19  (  2008  )  and 21  (  2011  )  , alongside Adele being interviewed by Norton .
